<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>仪表板</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>欢迎, <%= user.username %></h1>
    <p>您已成功登录.</p>
